step_deterministic.solution:
Theorem step_deterministic:
  deterministic step.
Proof with eauto.
  unfold deterministic. intros t t1 t2 H1 H2.
  generalize dependent t2.
  induction H1; intros t2 H2; inversion H2; subst; try reflexivity;
    try (exfalso; apply (value_is_nf _ (right _ _ H)); eexists; eassumption);
    try (exfalso; apply (value_is_nf _ (right _ _ H0)); eexists; eassumption);
    try (f_equal; apply IHH1; assumption).
Qed.
